70x2048.jpg 1770w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-rounded-island-250625-941-01.jpg\" alt=\"Get inspired by this light-filled kitchen with a cantilevered marble island, oak cabinetry, and clever storage solutions in a narrow urban footprint.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-rounded-island-250625-941-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-rounded-island-250625-941-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-rounded-island-250625-941-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-rounded-island-250625-941-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-rounded-island-250625-941-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eConnected directly to the kitchen, the living room continues the use of oak millwork in a custom media unit. This piece integrates with the kitchen cabinetry and includes built-in bench seating that doubles as storage. A wood-burning fireplace anchors the room, creating a natural gathering point, while a door opens to the backyard.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-rounded-island-living-room-250625-939-01.jpg\" alt=\"A custom oak media unit with built-in seating adds warmth and functionality to this open plan living space with a wood-burning fireplace.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-rounded-island-living-room-250625-939-01.jpg 192