r and reducing the need for artificial lighting.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-01.jpg\" alt=\"A sculptural staircase with a skylight above creates a vertical light shaft and maximizes space in this elegant three-level home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-01-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-01-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-01-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-01-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-01-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-02.jpg\" alt=\"A sculptural staircase with a skylight above creates a vertical light shaft and maximizes space in this elegant three-level home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-02.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-02-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-02-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-02-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-02-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-02-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-03.jpg\" alt=\"A sculptural staircase with a skylight above creates a vertical light shaft and maximizes space in this elegant three-level home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-03-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-03-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-03-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-03-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-03-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-04.jpg\" alt=\"A sculptural staircase with a skylight above creates a vertical light shaft and maximizes space in this elegant three-level home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-04.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-04-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-04-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-04-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-04-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-stairs-white-handrail-250625-945-04-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe children’s bedrooms are designed with thoughtful simplicity. Storage furniture and built-in closets keep the rooms tidy, while strategically placed windows offer framed views of the backyard or sky. Each space balances privacy with openness, offering room to rest, play, and grow.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-01.jpg\" alt=\"In this kids bedroom, storage furniture and built-in closets keep the room tidy, while strategically placed windows offer framed views of the backyard or sky. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-02.jpg\" alt=\"In this kids bedroom, storage furniture and built-in closets keep the room tidy, while strategically placed windows offer framed views of the backyard or sky. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-02-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-02-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-02-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/minimalist-kids-bedroom-design-250625-950-02-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAt the top of the stairs is the primary suite. The bedroom sits beneath the new A-frame roofline. Here, exposed Douglas Fir beams bring texture and depth, while high-level windows allow light to enter without sacrificing privacy. The room feels connected to nature yet protected, offering a sense of retreat.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-01.jpg\" alt=\"A-frame ceilings, timber beams, and framed views create a tranquil primary bedroom retreat above the trees.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-01-940x1253.jpg 940w, https: