oft, matte finishes keep the space feeling open and organized, with room for both daily use and long-term storage.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-03.jpg\" alt=\"This walk-in closet uses full-height cabinetry and soft finishes to make daily routines simple and beautiful.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-03-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-03-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-03-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-03-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-03-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn the ensuite bathroom, materials like stone and natural wood echo the palette used throughout the home. Large windows bring in soft natural light, and every detail, from the vanity to the fixtures, has been selected to promote calm and clarity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/primary-bedroom-suite-walk-in-closet-bathroom-250625-952-04.jpg\" alt=\"Natural stone, warm wood, and gentle daylight define this serene ensuite bathroom designed for daily retreat.\" srcset=\